data.comment: Wycombe kick-off to get the first-half underway.
Naby Sarr is booked for the away team.
In the minute 45, The ref's whistle signals the end of the first-half.
The second half is underway in Wycombe - Huddersfield with the kick-off.
David Wheeler is replacing Dominic Gape for the home team.
In the minute 68, Gareth Ainsworth is making the team's second substitution at Adams Park with Daryl Horgan replacing Scott Kashket.
Danny Ward is replacing Adama Diakhaby for Huddersfield at Adams Park.
Wycombe's Curtis Thompson has been booked in Wycombe.
In the minute 80, The home team replace Fred Onyedinma with Alex Samuel.
Wycombe make their fourth substitution with Garath McCleary replacing Dennis Adeniran.
Steve Martin blows to end the match. The final score is 0-0.
